-*- Indented-Text -*-



This directory contains example configurations for using the FIDOGATE
gateway and tosser:


dyff/		examples for current fidogate

orodruin/	orodruin.fido.de, 2:2452/110.2, 242:1000/5
		point configuration

win32/		Configuration examples for GNU-WIN32 environment.

point/		examples for "standard" Fido point configuration.

node/		examples for "standard" Fido node configuration.

rpm/		example config files for creating binary rpm.

See also the sendmail configuration files in ../sendmail/cf/.
